'''Meelweekian silk''' was a type of valuable [[Silk/Legends|silk]] that was used in fashioning luxurious furnishing and clothing. [[Celot Ratua Dil]] haggled with a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] on [[Trigalis/Legends|Trigalis]] over some meelweekian silk that had "fallen" from a commercial [[Hovervan/Legends|hovervan]] when [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] captured the gang and threw him in with them.

